data.description: Welcome to the best of BOTH worlds. The location of the character- filled property is ideal being that it is walking distance to restaurants and schools-- but is located at the  dead end of a quiet neighborhood with privacy.  This newly updated home with Smart Home features boasts 6 bedrooms with a newly remodeled high- end kitchen including soft close cabinets and drawers.  The kitchen leads into the formal dining room and also the open, light-filled family room. The open concept family room leads into a living room. New flooring recently installed throughout the main level and basement bedroom.   Natural light illuminates every area of the home with bay windows in the formal dining room and living room.  The basement has both an interior and an exterior entry with a full bathroom, full bedroom, media room, a kitchenette, and even unfinished storage areas.  The upstairs showcases all other 5 well- sized bedrooms with 2 full baths.  The primary suite has a walk- in closet and a sitting room that could be closed off as a nursery or office using the pocket doors.  The large, en-suite bathroom has a whirpool tub, with double vanities and shower.         You can take advantage of the privacy and weather and sit out on the brand new deck that overlooks the yard, professionally built play house, dog run, and other areas of the yard. Close to Truist Park, downtown Smyrna and Cobb schools.    More pictures coming soon.  Showings start Thursday.
